                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <div class="alert alert-warning">
                        <p><em>The "Combo" page allows you to view the key elements of the BluFractal System and the BluNeural System on one screen (if you have both Systems in your subscription plan.)</em></p>
                        <p><i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> &nbsp; <strong>Tip:</strong> You can use the daily BluFractal and BluNeural indicators for directional confirmation of your intra-day trades.</p>
                    </div>
                    <h4><i class="fa fa-list-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i> Indicators  </h4>
                    <p>BluFractal Near-Term Trend</p>
                    <p>BluNeural Current Zone</p>
                    <p>BluNeural Last Pivot</p>
                    <h4><i class="fa fa-list-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i> Charts  </h4>
                    <p>BluFractal (Near-Term)</p>
                    <p>BluNeural </p>
                </div>
                @*<div class="panel-footer">Panel Footer</div>*@
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

    </div>
